{"tid":1474380,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"政局不穩 傳阿里巴巴推遲在港上市","createTime":"2019-08-15T07:00:03.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-15T07:39:01.000Z","uid":144372,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"c867b00e4077e50b8592dd240c08fca2fffb41cb","tid":1474380,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:00:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/News.aspx?NewsID=NOW.958575&amp;NewsType=&amp;NewsSource=HK6\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.aastocks.com%2Ftc%2Fmobile%2FNews.aspx%3FNewsID%3DNOW.958575%26NewsType%3D%26NewsSource%3DHK6&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdoTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=16baef6c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.aastocks.com/tc/mobile/News.aspx?NewsID=NOW.958575&amp;NewsType=&amp;NewsSource=HK6</a><br />\n<br />\n據《紐約郵報》引述消息人士稱，由於香港發生大規模的反華示威，導致香港國際機場昨日採取管制出入安排，並已經吸引了世界的關注，故阿里巴巴集團(BABA)正在考慮推遲香港上市計劃。<br />\n<br />\n此前一直盛傳，阿里巴巴一直致力9月份在港作第二上市。而港交所(<a href=\"http://00388.HK\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2F00388.HK&d=%2BEgMKdsH73Wj%2FuX4aBpXdoTtxWFByFwd8BqLGIwhgUE%3D&h=ca48d1ca\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">00388.HK</a>)行政總裁李小加昨日(14日)表示，不會評論阿里巴巴上市進度，但相信阿里「最終會回家」。"},{"pid":"4bafdab9412f0424ac62f468bd6f6612fadfaa35","tid":1474380,"uid":2607,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:02:54.000Z","msg":"反華示威？"},{"pid":"1b028e3d4dbb91e9d9f71ef681d5e8c75505a171","tid":1474380,"uid":171992,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T07:03:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://na.cx/i/6yR8ycR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6yR8ycR.jpg&h=a587efad&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/08/14/141044_b70c4022f89dcf5617302fe3f20434af.jpeg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%